# LAND-007 B2c — legacy legal URL redirects.
#
# Existing external references (DPAs, partner contracts, Brevo SMTP signup,
# search engine indexes) point at the un-prefixed paths. 301 → EN (x-default)
# so we preserve link equity and don't break inbound links.
#
# Cloudflare Pages reads this file from the build output root and applies
# rules at the edge (no Worker round-trip). Status 301 = permanent —
# browsers/CDNs/search engines cache the redirect.
#
# See https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/redirects/

/privacy   /en/privacy   301
/terms     /en/terms     301
/cookies   /en/cookies   301
